column5: Dude, are you serious?! You know that guy and you taught him that?!

Nahhh just messing.  I played in a highschool band awhile with the guitarist/singer in this up and coming band.  James here was the most talented and has been producing some albums now.  If ya see them performing anywhere in Ontario be sure to go in and check 'em out.  They're out on tour opening with Matthew Good right now, but you can sometimes find them opening for the Hip, or just out there playing for themselves.   http://ca.youtube.com/watch?v=tzAGTQpriL4  Good solo in this vid.
I like using www.guitaretabs.com.  Has alot of goodies in there, check it out.  Party on Wayne
Checkout this guy  hes amazing....kinda jazz an blues love to play like that! http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HjXN3OLgoqs
Here's a new take on one of my favourites..Long Train Runnin'. http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ETHFjlAJaQA...feature=related

Here's a video of my buddy Justin and I doing a little jam.  Well... in this part it's just Justin.  He's working on the solo I taught him.  http://video.google.ca/videoplay?docid=400...vt=lf&hl=en  He's pretty good, check it out and enjoy.

Oh my! Thanks for that Bunk!!! I can now see me getting home from work tonight, and putting my guitar away and taking up sewing!!!!! I have a real love/hate relationship with guys like that... I love the way they play and Hate the way I do!!!! Thanks again! HH
It works fine for me. I doubt it's a virus. I think it's just spam trying to get you to purchase anti-virus software.
